    "body": "This is a first crack at a convenience function for creating a helper function to simplify CMake package definitions, namely to simplify the common but ugly and potentially error-prone idiom of\r\n```python\r\nargs.append('-DFOO=%s' % ('ON' if '+foo' in self.spec else 'OFF'))\r\n```\r\nto\r\n```python\r\nargs.append(self.define_from_variant('foo'))\r\n```",
